References: git-fixes

Originally was in the panel-simple, but belongs to panel-simple-dsi.

See arch/arm/boot/dts/nvidia/tegra114-roth.dts for more details.

Resolves the following warning:
```
Arch/arm/boot/dts/tegra114-roth.dt.yaml: panel@0: 'reg' does not match any of the regexes: 'pinctrl-[0-9]+'        From schema: Documentation/devicetree/bindings/display/panel/panel-simple.yaml
```

